                <h1>Golden Belt hosts mixer for local arts culture figures</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/bb7b03c7-f4d7-4c2e-b8a6-418c2d2ce8b2.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
